    <briefdescription>
<para>A class to use a simple map to combine styles. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>It uses a map of [current, overlay] -&gt; combined and uses <computeroutput><ref refid="classerbsland_1_1cterm_1_1_color_1abbc9a0612f92111e215ea38e8144eebe" kindref="member">Color::overlayWith</ref></computeroutput> to combine the colors. If a character is missing in the map, the overlay overwrites the current one. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
